CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774645562
OL,3,C'Who commissioned them?' Nesbitt
OL,4,Cquestions private firm's role in care
OL,5,Creviews
OL,7,FThe Health Minister has raised serious
OL,8,Fconcerns about the English-based
OL,9,Fprivate consultancy brought in by
OL,10,Fseveral health trusts to review
OL,11,Fcomplex care packages in Northern
OL,12,FIreland.
OL,14,FMike Nesbitt told Stormont's Health
OL,15,FCommittee on Thursday afternoon that
OL,16,Fhe has a number of questions about the
OL,17,Fuse of the company.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
