OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774645562
OL,3,C'Who commissioned them?' Nesbitt
OL,4,Cquestions private firm's role in care
OL,5,Creviews
OL,7,FLiaison Care was brought in by a
OL,8,Fnumber of trusts to review high cost
OL,9,Fand complex arrangements, and that
OL,10,Fincludes people moved out of Muckamore
OL,11,Fhospital following the abuse scandal,
OL,12,Fand many of whom now rely on intensive
OL,13,Fcommunity-based support.
OL,15,FThe Health Committee heard concerns
OL,16,Fabout how those reviews are being
OL,17,Fcarried out.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774645562
OL,3,C'Who commissioned them?' Nesbitt
OL,4,Cquestions private firm's role in care
OL,5,Creviews
OL,7,FDUP's Diane Dodds MLA said that she
OL,8,Fhas spoken to a number of families who
OL,9,Fwere deeply distressed after recent
OL,10,Fmeetings with the company.
OL,12,FShe said that they fear that these
OL,13,Freviews could lead to cuts in care or
OL,14,Fde-stabilise support packages.
OL,16,FMike Nesbitt said that reviewing care
OL,17,Fpackages is appropriate in principle
OL,18,Fto ensure efficiency and that right
OL,19,Fsupport is in place, but he said that
OL,20,Fhe does have questions about whether
OL,21,Fthe use of this company is appropriate.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774645562
OL,3,C'Who commissioned them?' Nesbitt
OL,4,Cquestions private firm's role in care
OL,5,Creviews
OL,7,FHealth Minister, Mike Nesbitt said:
OL,8,F"In terms of what is specifically
OL,9,Fhappening with this company, I have a
OL,10,Flot of questions which I have already
OL,11,Fbeen asking officials to get the
OL,12,Fcorrect answers to."
OL,14,FHe asked: "Who commissioned them?
OL,16,F"Why did they commission them?
OL,18,F"Why are we using a company that is
OL,19,Fnot based in Northern Ireland?
OL,21,F"What are their credentials?
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774645562
OL,3,C'Who commissioned them?' Nesbitt
OL,4,Cquestions private firm's role in care
OL,5,Creviews
OL,7,F"What are their competencies?
OL,9,F"There's maybe a question for NISCC,
OL,10,Fthe Northern Ireland Social Care
OL,11,FCouncil.
OL,13,F"Are all those operatives acceptable
OL,14,Fto NISCC?
OL,16,F"There may be a role for RQIA, so
OL,17,Fthere are a number of issues that need
OL,18,Fto be addressed."
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
